      "role": "user",
      "content": "got it. one more thing—what if the loss isn't just from weather? say it's something more suspicious, like theft or a container being 'lost' in a way that seems intentional or just weird/unexplained. how does the maritime law handle those kinds of murky or mysterious losses?",
